   <body>
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
      <h2>Cara menginstall Driver Printer MP C2003</h2>

   <h3>Tipe printer yang digunakan:</h3>
      <ul>
         <li>Jenis printer       : MP C2003</li>
         <li>Warm up time        : 19 detik</li>
         <li>Print/copy pertama  : full color: 7,6 detik ; B/W: 5,4 detik </li>
         <li>kecepatan kontinu   : full color: 7,6 detik ; B/W: 20PPM</li>
         <li>Memori: standard    : 1,5 GB MAX</li>
         <li>dimensi: (WxDxH)    : 587x685x788m</li>
      </ul>

<h3>Cara menginstall driver:</h3>
   <ol> 
    <li>Langkah pertama bukalah terminal yang ada di linux ubuntu</li>
    <li>Ketik command <code>sudo apt install mc</code></li>
    <img class="image" src="https://www.dropbox.com/pri/get/image/img1.png?_subject_uid=4618389344&amp;w=AADp9V-fHSj4xB33wwK_XDGSNjoKJl3tzSuLg9OV9Cw2rw" />
    <li>Setelah itu ketik command <code>sudo apt search ricoh</code></li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABtDKmq4KbAd0PU9EuE3Oi96Q8RgO9mvSQzS7-9emAtow-Kj-HZkGzWaD9Ef054Deldx53qXRBc8-NbZqpRBLL5pNqUIwopf57HCAu5AGOTbc0ZVZLVwm3N85TX2d-M09p_BBS06DsFNy0M2amq-RecVKNn_g95E6iBuphK38MfG8ioGrv5ullNU_73pXRcCYcyISP3uOA5OvQGhGBMxqlvQmdCffIAqxhKVyiH5CsdhAV1yEe4LM2JNF6JTl-6njh4GYYYVbiL5J6bxdVSLEO2z4cmG9JAqAlayB7S2RpNKuQMQCkrDSqlGR02lBODJPhZB0w1W12FxroLnO9LRAykOdDNA2Tjr-4NllIembjwcy9YHS0q_R_bWLXR3x-nlBWOvf_Ueuj8rWrbdq4gTeY-f/p.png" />
    <li>Lalu ketik command <code>sudo apt install printer-driver-sag-gdi</code></li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABuiy0-UqSmNNti_P8vgWhU70Wz7Hhzmsm5Dps6Si1hfZzFlG7lLj574qZ0ONft0IbmtGIJI5TQB1alXAVRb7ich2SFxizjvPnLBCFFDAp4fqqss4eK8AdRFLGjIirKEGjEgbpe4ka18ojS7tODvxEOrOmu362bhAXLQcjCGQvYcRv5Co9p_XSoK3WjasrJ9QE3R5G7NPdGs7bx4P2OjHF9EOljcspOWCKH7RwaXrHU2nZS6Wt9poot868frqjEdR4Fo9wWDarHXFU5A8NtRz8llAem1NztPcLBIZGsQ8kKNmlbHUSLGJFM_32XBC37BGLO0gx7AYfmJcOgFu2dWSR9OGW52AswMiPtGdwYwpU9U6SiBc31J50lH_m3MViTo5CcXEyXsjGF08nUv0KAz54tr/p.png" />
    <li>Setelah itu ketik command <code>sudo apt install cups</code></li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABuPY5OiXoyODf1NNO7g-QY84xXHazAttPpaFMP2jtvQcxHEIYNsOOz2jS3RQ596aYrzrDq26Aqu-HMNB2XIM_4NLh3wVpYFQBLyPcq4WW5KMZF5YAvVyUL6fybRgmBf3TBuNIyTfWmAZSRs16KGQarP9iQW4dHV3rZrkhnhsv56iPHXNB_ZXpxYQB3ZuziEgUGKJ3PD_vbgtJjGdFfhgM7oCBVXNEWTfy2rAL5ynrhkgUNrgejkxCGHiDRM_qkdefRzmCTdJ9NpRd7_oOfDZv-4UV22mmuNzLJO7iPaoeM1IbbsbNABrycH7FKHWwOL16MnLSCxHxdq1xyoZojLHNMLwwJLhGRtF7slOBldHI__EbC_dtG82jo4KKgh2Ssxk74/p.png" />
    <li>Lalu ketik <code>sudo systemctl status cups</code></li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABuZXh8Xy4KO98XHcYijgY4SOWtZKExYYlhvFhJMb_BzUCAwtE0G6ZjDh5FUdVtE5w58Xsa3QE0VgotLCZ9WgC2dmfPseT7sKud3GlwoEszIyhn2kY13ZhjQvn4oTQoGs6HR1SmpMo9GJe4EKGrkI8PYbmjvxl2jEsLmW2putnG9bgzUWz3xgAohFjUWE1aiy9GZLsjMfK98XlhBmBwIrxYBuPBmyiAje7KIrYs2M91YYmpivmh6rnCSsUR9IXgZLbgHcv4G7XTFrNJctwh6zpvfecEtzvWZxdRr1xKrsympC7_gEItz6_HjJoH18cij9KQeUUagn5ZZm7ezR2mExUi05j6LQHQwwq3GiWrW-4E4Rh9OA3OpSJ9TcDkZr3mYdy0/p.png" />
    <li>Jika hasil command sudah menandakan active/running maka lantut ketahap berikutnya</li> 
    <li>Tahap berikutnya buka web di search engine kalian dengan keyword “localhost:631”</li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABu6Dn9rVbnEMTKZqEr_cGRDOFoBUADigIKpL1gn2ordwsJez2XKDl3UDjiQAcYMnTJZXvivQEYyHjD3PmhgoULtBT9Nb4qEb7oQXiviYG8k7U-Jq36O5TqbEIyFN_yPK4_VIADpTEFYYnqaaihJenYVgJnDrV38ZHLoevoQoGkBCGx4rfjDiorff9QDS69tPba1Oy1ffNbjTjKAOCuOluJ-2O9DcdMZkrHZyKMQv7Am7gtMmGFTmGMiuP4KH0FV7D9QV9u0367Tm98Bqy6-5YPun-de0JSvbMBmb6nghYFJoNNkX5i55odFIvrp55yCoNCq7LkBHvt2ybzDJRsDHtG2uPoPmL378gd5RPMsnFCfpeHHxmDzg9yVnhU8mBIqZjU/p.png" />
    <li>Lalu klik pada opsi printers yaitu “add printer”</li>
    <li>Jika sudah cari nama printer yang akan kalian sambungkan di area "discovered network printer"</li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABvar_0mVw3by0p1REXFC2cavdAoYcpRUECO_8GN6afDLddYHGmW_bpBdMzZx1UpUYS5GOSPmL1njdXTXw2tfq2mHUv2hjtYQQhHKUoE21mg4A148BqcicFGjCt4bC6sjD9ruHcF6ogJUc8EhMCgmW5hgEPSt1gTBbAe-2KaWmQE9bY96estBAIa-Rirgt47IgPbr0sYW7Nto_t8u056hYr7tbvrBChwywWEP0HJ4Gzua4PkJvsTWcoO2c-zNLT8l78SStaAyvREx5i4cGIF-cDtrPYd69wF2KmVfSPM66U_ckXcVFK7uVYYjxaqlShHCA3SaXvPjqnuJPJ9-31r11ULoTaTuCH8kHrjlgbOtV2yJcVMuEKl88jDYP12hrkZYg8XcLPcp8-CDgCZFd6zWxWs/p.png" />
    <li>Pilih model printer yang akan kalian samungkan ke komputer anda</li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABt-QGpGW3LOtkHBpPwYryMlmPdITwQcT69FahZfWa5IGXcEXVkG-rH6JoUzJqYssNPf-MZy3TJ1xMSSO-pGX-15jhaqATkgs0dJFf-d6Dl1kLRNP5hxvyeWPru8NtpxIwqE9FxkzbWwqR9hvQ2I0owAfdbCeEA5GAidLubupdgp0VlKaWq1bnQPdFlegPXiRByo4Lav_TEITk-2J1VCCLgcRSpfCC2GtwxYZKwckoTZKeNb5UstVcYoizV7hkuwNZNDCiUzT-CL92idTZRUAUEPfx8bNYL7neoGnfopasxQ3l85zXYjlsqMrwo4V8JT1ddIRMR6qmQL5ZTtoxy9lqeoa2pKnXVaAmXBAueHRX8Lah04gZhzYmIqhQiFa4WZ6vXbL9CRGXbHAgs-SetzhY3k/p.png" />
    <li>Lalu klik add printer</li>
    <img class="image" src="https://previews.dropbox.com/p/thumb/ABsT4oSyl9XaR1DgQGhrx5srvAw1WabiHXxz4YBzCsWZsjJL8NlU6Sd6GnbSognwY-KYvEKSjv8jECxQH9InIp1DIJcXJFH_NT_JxO_n99nGsukHEEN7Wq4WW7vjn1YsPheo942S-oCQSlJ7DijGlKDCYYoUk8TYoEJr3cBGqOv58mtXErxbLsR0cv0inNvFEMJtREZ92hz0YO8wKwXxrl0sDLYuy10XpmyMX4-PgJolbBAwLoqrwhs2WCX3JbgeipP247bPrZ2rLRW6xqOwQlREvooot5iGdRv1bb0xOJlwP1TbVzRSuzTwnGZzgK__a1AzF-80cu-uPKOn3z3HQL5YTp7eI6jEKm8LsK_2aMTtiEO2g29ML049wEcCZSlnYs4/p.png" />
    <li>Printer siap digunakan</li>
   </ol>


